data.description:
Step inside to discover a warm and welcoming atmosphere, where the stylish flooring creates a seamless flow throughout the space. The open-concept design allows for easy entertaining and comfortable living, making this property a true haven for its occupants.

One of the standout features of this residence is the addition of solar panels, offering both an eco-friendly and cost-effective energy solution. Embrace sustainable living while enjoying the benefits of reduced utility costs and a smaller environmental footprint.

The exterior of the property is equally impressive, with a well-maintained yard providing a perfect setting for outdoor activities and relaxation. The combination of modern updates and classic appeal makes 105 Oakland St a unique and desirable home in the heart of Waco.

Conveniently located in a sought-after neighborhood, this property offers easy access to local amenities, schools, and parks. Whether you're a first-time homebuyer or looking to upgrade to a more sustainable lifestyle, this is the perfect place to call home.

Don't miss the opportunity to make this home yours. Schedule a viewing today and experience the perfect blend of modern living and timeless comfort. 
MOTIVATED SELLERS!! This property also qualifies for 100% financing!!
